 modify the current order set to reflect some of the finer points so as to avoid developing and maintaining a separate order set for Retinal. Please advise. Dr. Greer Gieger is the Retinal Surgeon sponsor of this order set.?1214926239?H521379?Tina H Hamilton\n\n6/25/08 email Amitabh K Bharadwaj/CA/KAIPERM\n1.  I noticed that the wording for the postop order for HTN control isnt quite right.  Here it is: \n \n\"Check bp every 20 minutes postoperatively.  If systolic > 160 or diastolic > 100, please notify anesthesia for bp control.  Discontinue blood pressure checks after 3 hours.\" \n?',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(2144,0,'N',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',2546590,NULL,'NEW OS Bariatric SUR: Hosp Day One ; create per attachment',NULL,'OS',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,'L','N','H','0','Bariatric Day One',NULL,'','','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,'NOWRK','Res','SUR','KPHC CN IP ORDERSETS',NULL,'End User Applications','KPHC Inpatient MD/CRNA/Midwife Content','Order Set - MD','','L','N','N',' ','0','NR',' ','N','PERI','0','0','0','0','0','0','0',NULL,NULL,'2008-11-19 11:57:22','2008-12-24 11:58:22','2008-12-24 10:39:50','2008-12-29 07:53:50','2008-05-05 15:40:20',' ','','','','','','','','',964,NULL,201,201,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','2008-11-19 00:00:00','2008-10-15 00:00:00','2008-10-30 00:00:00','2008-11-05 00:00:00','2008-11-12 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2008-11-10 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'2008-11-12 00:00:00','2008-11-12 00:00:00','2008-11-19 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2008-11-21 00:00:00','2008-11-24 00:00:00','2008-11-26 00:00:00','2008-11-26 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'190