l be both additions to and subtractions from the current single vascular order set.   \nDr Mentakis and myself are the contact persons for this change.  Any communication re this request should also be copied to Drs. Ram Ramachandra  and Michael B Peterson \n***end***\n\n<BR><BR>2009-02-13 - Tina H Hamilton - TIGR review 2/10/09, and follow up call to Maggie Mentakis.\nSR lacks final content, agreement to reassign back to SSC with note to submit separate SRs when final content for selected ordersets is ready. Send note to Dr Kashtan to provide update<BR><BR>',982,874,NULL,NULL,NULL),(2483,0,'N',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','',3341016,NULL,'SRO KPHC IP MCH',NULL,'SR',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,'L','0','H','0','',NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,'NICE','Res','0','KPHC CN IP CLINDOC BUS',NULL,'End User Applications','KPHC Inpatient Nursing / Non-MD','Flowsheet Row/Template','','L','N','N',' ',NULL,'NR','N','N','NICU','0','0','0','0','0','0','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-04-28 16:47:41','2009-05-10 01:20:12','2009-05-11 07:50:01','2009-02-05 13:34:01',' ',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'','','',1030,NULL,197,197,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-02-06 10:04:00','2009-02-06 10:04:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'SRO KPHC IP MCH:  When in IV Assessment and adding a LDA--Peripheral the site Umbilical needs to be removed.  This is not an anatomically correct option for a peripheral site.  Please also add