mmediate hypersensitivity, both Gent and clinda are necessary. In addition to changing the subsection from single select to multiselect, decision support language under the title, \"Recommendation: Clindamycin PLUS Gentamicin\" is added to help users make the correct choices.\nAdditionally, ACOG recommends adding Flagyl is bacterial vaginosis is suspected to prevent cuff cellulitis.\n\nPhysician Sponsor Name:\nElliot Morrison, MD Santa Rosa Domain Lead\n\nDo',NULL,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(2609,0,'N',1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Maggie Mentakis','',3687206,NULL,'OS PeriOp Day of Surgery SUR 414233: Nursing orders; change preselect and remove, see descripton',NULL,'OS',NULL,'Stage',NULL,'0','L','R','M','D','void',NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'',NULL,'NICE','Res','SUR','KPHC CN IP ORDERSETS',NULL,'End User Applications','KPHC Inpatient MD/CRNA/Midwife Content','Order Set - MD','','L','N','N',' ',NULL,'NR',' ','N','PERI','0','0','0','0','0','0','0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-07-21 10:05:01','2009-07-22 09:28:49','2009-07-23 11:10:00','2009-05-28 12:39:25',' ',NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,'','','',1058,NULL,201,201,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-06-02 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,'1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','2009-07-17 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00','1900-01-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2009-06-01 08:49:00','2009-07-17 10:50:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'OS PeriOp Day of S